title: Can't see club I own
body: For the last few months haven't been able to see the club I own, the club still exists as my friends are still in it and the club tag shows up on them in game.

replies.body: There may be a syncing issue between the club and your account.  What's your club name and tag, as long as it's appropriate?  I'll take a look and see if I can refresh it for you!
Refreshed!  Relog then you should be good to go!
